Now in most movie and tv adaptations they make these two one and the same, also the story is usually pushed together as one and the same (looking glass world is not Wonderland) so it would be cool if because the Queen of Hearts lost her throne in the first movie, she calls herself The Red Queen now that she's in the wilderness.
